        {
            "title": "鈾為何重新成為戰略性大宗商品",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yce0ozLKO.N1eYrD2l6htQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC9209J_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 根據BCA Research的特別報告,隨著結構性供應短缺和能源安全擔憂加劇,加上伊朗持續衝突的影響,鈾的牛市正在加強,這種大宗商品正朝著持久的長期上漲趨勢邁進。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>地緣政治衝擊強化看漲理由</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">BCA Research的分析師強調,伊朗戰爭正成為鈾板塊的力量倍增器。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">除了核電作為對沖化石燃料波動性的更廣泛推動力之外,這場衝突還特別擾亂了核燃料循環所需的關鍵投入,包括硫磺供應。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-020eaeac-c760-34c8-b9ec-50daa52fbbaa-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新出現的限制正在收緊本已岌岌可危的市場,BCA指出,供應安全敘事已成為公用事業公司尋求鎖定長期合約的主要驅動力。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>持續的結構性短缺</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管近期產量有所增長,但報告強調全球需求仍繼續超過可用供應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">結構性短缺因全球對核能的政策支持浪潮而加劇,各國旨在實現雄心勃勃的脫碳目標,同時確保可靠的基載電力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此外,幾個關鍵需求驅動因素的勢頭正在增強。推動核能擴張不再僅僅是為了減碳;它越來越多地與人工智能和數據中心基礎設施的高耗電需求聯繫在一起。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">結合全球政策一致性,這些因素表明鈾目前的緊張局勢不僅僅是週期性高峰,而是這種大宗商品進入新戰略時代的標誌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%88%BE%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E6%88%90%E7%82%BA%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%E6%80%A7%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%97%E5%95%86%E5%93%81-005853804.html",
