        {
            "title": "伊朗逆轉過境重開決定 荷莫茲海峽航運再陷混亂",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FSohemaPO_oD8FNraAnbyA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_6_M_1440048362.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 荷莫茲海峽恢復正常能源運輸的短暫希望已被突然澆熄,伊朗在宣布開放這條關鍵海上要道僅數小時後,再次對其實施嚴格管制。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>命運逆轉</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這條承載全球約五分之一液化天然氣(LNG)供應的戰略水道,在週六迎來了一波試圖通過的油輪。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗外交部長阿巴斯·阿拉格奇週五宣布,配合黎巴嫩停火協議,該海峽已\"完全開放\",這一聲明引發了這些船隻的過境嘗試。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,這種樂觀情緒很快就破滅了。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3e3f136e-f2f4-3e06-bd2f-ef6d24d44d55-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">航運數據和海事安全報告證實,伊朗炮艇攔截並向數艘商船開火,其中包括至少一艘貨櫃船和一艘油輪,且事前未發出無線電警告。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一突然轉變發生在美國總統唐納德·川普澄清之後,儘管有外交姿態,但美國對伊朗港口的海上封鎖仍將\"全面實施\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">德黑蘭迅速作出報復,伊朗安全官員表示,他們將把美國持續的封鎖視為違反停火協議,從而有效地使海峽的臨時重開作廢。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>供應鏈停滯</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由此產生的混亂迫使數艘在卡塔爾裝載的液化天然氣油輪掉頭或在波斯灣停泊,這本將是自2月下旬衝突爆發以來首次大規模天然氣貨物過境。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該水道的實際關閉繼續造成嚴重的供應瓶頸,尤其是對那些嚴重依賴石油和天然氣運輸以確保能源安全的亞洲新興市場而言。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師警告稱,華盛頓和德黑蘭發出的矛盾信號正在加劇本已動盪的局勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於保險公司仍對持續存在的襲擊、水雷和攔截威脅保持警惕,該海峽的\"高風險\"狀態依然存在,使全球能源市場和基本燃料供應處於極度不確定的狀態。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E9%80%86%E8%BD%89%E9%81%8E%E5%A2%83%E9%87%8D%E9%96%8B%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A-%E8%8D%B7%E8%8E%AB%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E8%88%AA%E9%81%8B%E5%86%8D%E9%99%B7%E6%B7%B7%E4%BA%82-002205431.html",
